<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>简易图片生成网站</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }

        input,
        button {
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px;
        }

        img {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>简易图片生成网站</h1>
    <p>请输入图片的宽度和高度，然后点击生成按钮。</p>
    <input type="number" id="width" placeholder="宽度" value="400">
    <input type="number" id="height" placeholder="高度" value="300">
    <button onclick="generateImage()">生成图片</button>
    <div id="imageContainer"></div>

    <script>
        function generateImage() {
            const width = document.getElementById('width').value;
            const height = document.getElementById('height').value;
            const imageUrl = `https://dummyimage.com/${width}x${height}/ff0000/ffffff`;
            const img = document.createElement('img');
            img.src = imageUrl;
            img.alt = '生成的图片';
            const imageContainer = document.getElementById('imageContainer');
            imageContainer.innerHTML = '';
            imageContainer.appendChild(img);
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>
    